snippet.title: Shivaleela - Official Trailer | Divakar S | Ashok Jayram | Manjamma Jogthi | Dhanushkumar D Shetty
snippet.description:
#shivaleela #transgendermovie #ashokjayram #dachhudivu #bmanjammajogthi #dhanushkumardshetty #trailer

This Vedio : 

A group of rowdies are targeting the Transgender's and intending 
to push them into prostitution. With such malicious intent, the rowdies are 
trying to catch the Transgender's. The Transgender's are facing various 
problems in leading their lives. A young man named Acharya understands 
the hardships of the Transgender's. He understands the plan of the 
rowdies. Acharya fights with the rowdies to protect the Transgender's. 
Then the Transgender's go to the Janata Court. Then the 
Transgender's go to the Janata Court. After hearing their plight, the court 
immediately forms a committee to stand up for them. 

This is not just to create History  -  to correct history entire system

Story - Screenplay - Dialogues - Choreography - Fight - Produced & Directed by ASHOK JAYRAM

Assistant Director : Lijo Thomas

Cast:

Actor : Divakar S
Starring : Padhmashree Dr B Manjamma Jogthi 
Negative Lead Role : Dhanushkumar D Shetty
Actor : MS Umesh
Actor : Moogu Suresh

Crew:

Director of Photography : Praveen Shetty
Editor : Rajesh Chavan
Music Director : Ramesh Krishna
DI : Kishore Kumar Akkana
DTS : Chandrashekar

Banner : Jayram Creations

snippet.title: The Kaali Song - Lyrical | Mark | Kichcha Sudeepa | V Kartikeyaa | Ajaneesh B Loknath
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe ðŸ‘‰ https://bit.ly/Saregama_Kannada

Presenting the lyrical of ''The Kaali Song'' from "Mark" starring Kichcha Sudeepa and others. Directed by V Kartikeyaa. Music Composed by Ajaneesh B Loknath. T.G. Thyagarajan presents - Produced by Sendhil Thyagarajan and Arjun Thyagarajan.

Song Credits:
Name: The Kaali song
Song composed arranged & programmed by B.Ajaneesh Loknath
Singer :Aniruddha Sastry 
Lyrics:  Aniruddha Sastry 
Chorus: Brinda, Aishwarya Daruri, Maneesha Pandranki, Dasari Meghanaa Naidu, Abhishek M R, Satvik S Rao, Bhargav H C, Abhijith Sudheer, Anirudha Bhargava, Skandesh S, Gagan Puranik. 
Keyboard: B. Ajaneesh Loknath , SharanRao
Rhythms: B Ajaneesh Loknath, Andruson ,  SharanRao 
Song Mixed & Mastered by Pukhraj Sonkar @inhouse studio
Assistant: Dipesh Dhruw, Mumbai
Music Production : C R Bobby, B Ajaneesh Loknath, Abbs Studios, Bangalore
Lyrical video: GOD MODE STUDIOZ

Movie Credits:
Banner: Sathya Jyothi Films & Kichcha Creatiions
T.G. Thyagarajan Presents
Produced by: Sendhil Thyagarajan, Arjun Thyagarajan

Shankar Nagu S, David Prashanth, Premkumar
DoP Team: Mariswamy YT Halli, Madhusudana B R, Umesh, Sai Raghavendra K

Lyrics:
Intro -
Rudra Roopa Lakshyam
Kathora Ghora Deeksham
Raktapaata Krityam
Karaala Kaali Drishyam

Pallavi
Omkaara Ninna Hoonkaara
Samhaara Maado Shreekaara
Aadishakti Paraashaktiye
Ninna Sero Maarga Nija Bhaktiye
Jeeva Heeruvavara Aasege
Neenu Needabekide Muktiye..
Kaali Namma Kapaadalu Nee Baareya
Kaali Shoolavaagi Banda Markandeya

Bhadra Kaali Baa
Rudra Kaali Baa
Mahaa Kaali Baa
Are Baaro Baaro Maark
Maark â€¦

Charana -
Yuddhabhoomili Gharjisuvantha
Rudra Roopa Taalo Durgeya Doota
Dharmavannu Sthaapisuvantha
Amshavaagi Bandano Ee Bhagavanta
Novanu Nunguva Shakti Innu Nannallillamma
Nannaya Antya Kaano Munna Ninna Nodabekamma

Kaali Namma Kapaadalu Nee Baareya
Kaali Shoolavaagi Banda Markandeya
Omkaara Ninna Hoonkaara
Samhaara Maado Shreekaara

Bhadra Kaali Baa
Rudra Kaali Baa
Mahaa Kaali Baa
Are Baaro Baaro Maark
Maark â€¦

snippet.title: Shinchan and Franklin  Celebrate Christmas with Santa Claus in GTA 5
snippet.description:
In this video Shinchan and Franklin  Celebrate Christmas with Santa Claus in GTA 5

In this fun and festive GTA 5 story mod, Franklin transforms his house into a Christmas wonderland, decorating it with sparkling lights and a massive Christmas tree. ðŸŒŸ

Franklin wants to spread joy to all his gang members, so he goes on a gift-hunting adventure! First, he surprises Shinchan with an amazing 3-wheeled blue bike, then grabs a super muscle car equipped with an RPG rocket launcher! ðŸš—ðŸ’¥ But the holiday fun doesnâ€™t stop there â€” Franklin also buys delicious cake and wine for everyone in the gang. ðŸŽ‚ðŸ·

Things get magical when Franklin meets Santa Claus on his rooftop! ðŸŽ… Santa tells him about his second sleigh, parked near the Los Santos Dam Observatory. Franklin sets off on a mission to find this beautiful sleigh and bring it home.

Finally, itâ€™s time for the big celebration! Franklin wakes up the gang, hands out all the gifts, and invites Chop and Shinchan for a thrilling ride on the sleigh. Together, they soar across the Los Santos skyline, enjoying the festive spirit and the joy of friendship. âœ¨

Donâ€™t miss this epic Christmas story full of laughter, surprises, and GTA 5 chaos!

ðŸŽ If you enjoyed the video, hit LIKE ðŸ‘, SUBSCRIBE ðŸ””, and share it with your friends to spread the Christmas cheer!

snippet.description:
Every beat of this song carries the pawprints of love, a rhythm woven with the joy of Hara, Suji, and Jojo. They are not just pets, but the melody of our family â€” the laughter in our days, the harmony in our hearts, and the purest chorus of unconditional love. In their presence, life feels brighter, softer, and endlessly more beautiful. This song is for them, our eternal companions, our familyâ€™s sweetest joy.

Toi Mure Vuti ( female dog )
Moi tore Vota ( male dog ) 
Mane moi tor maiki 
Toi Mure Mota 
Toi Mure prem 
Toi mure prio 
lagile di toi gali lathi mari hoday mok 
kintu nidbi mok eri moromore tiri 
dile toi morom hoi jang moi gorom
ami duyo kukur xeye manuh puhe 
pohora diu khaba dile ami vuku 
anke - Vau Bhau bhaw vaw bhaou vao bhao bhu vu bou voou vouu song baou bau vau vau song

kiman je dukh pao dekhi kene amar monot 
logor logot modor logot parile to sahor logot 
kati kene dao logot boil kore pani logot soup khai momo logot jai sabi Nagaland ot dam dor kukur logot ek kilo 2 kilo ki ase poisa logot tula tuli poisa utham party korim friendor logot 
morbo sob salla joli poki norokot fridge ot thoy amar mankho nije morok borofot.
thanda lagi sordi lagi korobate fasi lagi

Sri Godadevi Chalisa Telugu | Sri Lakshmi Devi Chalisa | Dhanurmasam Special | Goddess Andal Songs | Goddess Lakshmi Devi Songs 

Sri Godadevi Chalisa Telugu and Godadevi Songs Telugu glorify the divine devotion of Andal Devi through soulful Andal Devi Chalisa and Sri Andal Devotional Songs Telugu. During the sacred Dhanurmasam Special Songs, devotees immerse themselves in Godadevi Bhakti Songs and traditional Andal Dhanurmasam Songs, offering heartfelt prayers. The serene flow of Vishnu Bhakti Telugu Songs blends beautifully with Dhanurmasam Pooja Songs, creating a sacred atmosphere. Through Sri Godadevi Bhakthi Geethalu, devotees celebrate pure devotion and divine grace during the auspicious Dhanurmasam.

Listen to the divine Sri Godadevi Chalisa, dedicated to Goddess Godadevi (Andal), the eternal consort of Lord Vishnu. This special devotional song is offered during the sacred month of Dhanurmasam, an auspicious time for bhakti, vratham, and Vishnu worship.

Listen to the best collection of Sri Lakshmi Devi and Sri Godadevi Bhakthi Songs, dedicated to the divine goddesses of wealth, prosperity, devotion, and spiritual blessings.

These powerful devotional songs help bring peace, positivity, abundance, and divine grace into your life. Ideal for daily prayers, Margasiramasam worship, festivals, and meditation.

Ramba Ho-Ho-Ho Samba Ho-Ho-Ho is a high-energy, fun-filled track that brings unstoppable groove.
A lively song made to dance, celebrate, and turn up the mood.

Music Director: Indiwar
Cast: Ranjeeta, Raj Babbar, Shammi Kapoor, Deepak Parashar, Prema Narayan

Lyrics:
Hoâ€¦ tu mera jaaneman
Jaaneman main teri mehbooba

Hoâ€¦ muskura, muskura gham mein
Tum kyun dooba? kyun dooba?

Living, we are living
Dancing, we are dancing
For the peopleâ€¦ we love
Love-love-love-love

Ramba ho-ho, ho, ho
Samba ho-ho, ho, ho
Ramba ho-ho, ho, ho
Samba ho-ho, ho, ho

Main naachoon, tum naacho
Jitni tum pyaar se jiloge
Utni hi zindagi

Ramba ho-ho, ho, ho
Samba ho-ho, ho, ho
Ramba ho-ho, ho, ho
Samba ho-ho, ho, ho

Hoâ€¦ duniya mein logon ke
Mele ye aayenge, jaayenge

Hoâ€¦ yaaro sang mil ke hum
Jhoomenge, jhoomenge, gaayenge

Shining, stars are shining
Singing, yeah yeah, singing
For peopleâ€¦ we love
Love-love-love-love

Rambaâ€¦ sambaâ€¦
Ho-ho, ho, ho
Samba ho-ho, ho, ho

Main naachoon, tum naacho..!
